de_canal_beta - May 20 2005
================================================================
Title                   : de_canal
Filenames               : de_canal.txt (this readme file)
                          de_canal.nav (bot file)
                          de_canal.bsp (the level itself)

Author                  : Flum
Email Address           : lars@johanssonart.com
Web Page		: www.johanssonart.com
Description             : A small and simple bomb map. 2-32 players
================================================================

* Play Information *

New Sounds              : no
New Graphics            : no
New Music               : no

* Construction *

Base                    : new level from scratch
Editor(s) used          : 3ds MAX 7, the GLB exporter and Hammer
Known Bugs              : Bad framerate in some areas and poor 
                          optimazation from my part, sorry :/
                          Pleas send me a mail if (when?) you find
                          any bugs :)
Build Time              : two weeks on and off
Compile machine         : p4, 3.0GHz, 1024mb ram
Compile Time            : 3:35 seconds

Summary of the level
====================
Tried to make a small but enyojable map that has sniperspots 
aswell as close quater fighting. The idea behind the map is 
that you should be able to play it with a small group of people 
and still have a fun time. The layout is keep simple but 
with a clear flow. it is planed so that the CT will have 
a second or so to setup the defence before the T arrive. a small 
but very importent advantage.
Enyoj! :)


Shoutout's
==========
LoveMeister, thanks for all the playtest and good ideas.
btw download and try out The LoveMeisters map de_haywire. :)

Thank you!
Flum
